{"tid":2426169,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"東京奧運情勢走向負面：日本藝人陸續退出聖火傳遞火炬手風潮","createTime":"2021-02-28T00:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T17:32:26.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"929cb9aaec454747d7bde88dd1d74c072751ce45","tid":2426169,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/tokyo-olympic-torchbearer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Ftokyo-olympic-torchbearer%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=e94f10c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/tokyo-olympic-torchbearer/</a><br />\n<br />\n延期一年，現預定於2021年7月23日舉行的東京奧運會，距離現在還有差不多4個月，大會的重點會前活動聖火傳遞也在進行最後調整，但現時它正卻變得非常不明朗。沖縄縣代表玉城Tina、石川縣代表常盤貴子已宣布退出火炬手。另外福島縣代表斎藤工也盛傳會退出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/asahicom/status/1365299856428834825?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasahicom%2Fstatus%2F1365299856428834825%3Fs%3D21&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=0fae3d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasahicom%2Fstatus%2F1365299856428834825%3Fs%3D21&h=8d306afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/asahicom/status/1365299856428834825?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n在2月26日，常盤貴子與玉城Tina分別在下午與晚上各自傳出退出消息。兩人的經理人事務所都聯絡了縣政府，理由同樣地以工作繁忙，日程不能配合，聽起來帶點弦外之音的感覺。另外還有名歌手五木宏也在同日公報退出。而在2月27日，福島縣當地媒體也得到了縣代表斎藤工辭退的消息，理由相信也是因為疫情關係，工作日程更改以致時間不能配合。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fminyu/status/1365480699549995009?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffminyu%2Fstatus%2F1365480699549995009%3Fs%3D21&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=0c298242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffminyu%2Fstatus%2F1365480699549995009%3Fs%3D21&h=7a79bf47\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fminyu/status/1365480699549995009?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n其實早在2月初，自東京奧運組委會前會長森喜朗的炎上發言後，著名搞笑藝人田村淳已宜布退出聖火傳遞。但他的理由是針對森喜朗的發言。發言首先有「不論疫情什麼狀況，東京奧運都要舉辦」，還有「藝人拿聖火在田裡跑」，田村淳不解以上發言，同時也認為疫情平息是重要的，有需要的話便延期。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/atsushilonboo/status/1358068308629622784?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fatsushilonboo%2Fstatus%2F1358068308629622784%3Fs%3D21&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=959d5eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fatsushilonboo%2Fstatus%2F1358068308629622784%3Fs%3D21&h=388f52ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/atsushilonboo/status/1358068308629622784?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n之前森喜朗也發表了「女性多的理事會，都會變得更浪費時間」的驚人發言，這也直接導致東京奧運1,000名義工辭退。(詳情請看：東京奧委會會長森喜朗：驚人「針對女性」不當發言 引發災難性聲討)<br />\n<br />\n對於奧運的負面走向，已經慢慢成形，火炬手名單上的石原聰美、指原莉乃、窪田正孝、伊藤英明到底會否一個個表示「因工作日程關係」而不能配合聖火傳遞活動呢？"},{"pid":"ae4bb0fd420bde0be8570184f741b00f72ad129e","tid":2426169,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:04:05.000Z","msg":"日本都有今日"},{"pid":"808e629230b188818a973da7fd939e44c07d5da7","tid":2426169,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"如果喺支那，全部顛覆國家政權拉鳩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 以日本嚟講，其實森喜朗講嘢根本冇問題<br />\n自民黨自己都歧視女人啦，高層會議女人唔准發言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac971aeef5d2b94d788d15b0f9604b9bf270e01","tid":2426169,"uid":305638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"封殺av吖拿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52e61338bc64e71ba1c22387712656c566516f0","tid":2426169,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"火鉅手冇結衣bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501a1ecc0a62b5e9e8fc7c86beca8e35110c7784","tid":2426169,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得幾啱，但事實係難聽啲"},{"pid":"877d5eae6f2fb3cf496212960a16592b78300758","tid":2426169,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"以為D 藝人怕感染, 所以唔去傳聖火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c81b00c7bffd40e373d422745946681ce356b7","tid":2426169,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽既說話你想唔想聽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dc32382fe9a24f36e84f641057b8c4e8744463","tid":2426169,"uid":255926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn1.diodeo.kr/cdn/webzine/2016/04/04/20160404140743_xnchbrxx.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.diodeo.kr%2Fcdn%2Fwebzine%2F2016%2F04%2F04%2F20160404140743_xnchbrxx.gif&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3pS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=6b4a63f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn1.diodeo.kr/cdn/webzine/2016/04/04/20160404140743_xnchbrxx.gif</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jh6NvE0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjh6NvE0.gif&h=a3c328f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湊崎紗夏會唔會返日本"},{"pid":"7349da8512a6654ba1a91b465de86c1995a2ce53","tid":2426169,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"又話日本人好團結?"},{"pid":"af681f749d357d044334e7dee9076b0d5ef72e4e","tid":2426169,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢把啦<br />\n再將矛頭指向支共<br />\nIf you got the balls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d16d6e853de51fd1d3d5e172fb34a54026a5f0","tid":2426169,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac971aeef5d2b94d788d15b0f9604b9bf270e01","tid":2426169,"uid":305638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"封殺av吖拿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"天譴"},{"pid":"1f8a503b22ff5c50cc6d5da74181f1dc1a8bac43","tid":2426169,"uid":268516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"但而家換左個女人上位<br />\n仲未嬲完？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n性火而家話改到神秘咁進行<br />\n一人多聚集就取消<br />\n做賊咁就不如算鳩數"},{"pid":"863187d953321d3f9cc2424208f2573e0affad49","tid":2426169,"uid":238214,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:32:26.000Z","msg":"東奥 閉門比賽的話<br />\n不如取消算啦 蝕到hihi"}]}